Description:Provides functions to visualise node support values from
    multiple independent phylogenomic analyses simultaneously on a
    single reference tree using the rug plot method. Although
    researchers routinely run multiple phylogenomic analyses,
    they publish one tree and hide the rest in supplementary
    materials, yet no dedicated R tool exists to visualise node
    support across multiple analyses, leaving researchers unable
    to communicate phylogenomic uncertainty transparently in a
    single publication figure.
